      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KING ZEAL (5) shapes as hard to beat after winning last start over the 440m at this track in a solid 24.85. Hot win latest and looks the one to beat again. JACKY LEGS (8) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 440m behind Nangar Noah (25.24) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from three attempts. Warrants plenty of respect. LITTLE ESMERALDA (1) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fourth by 5 lengths (25.20). Expected to run well. CONDO BANDIT (2) is another with top-three prospects.",
